title: november 10: record breakers
description:
In this episode of 365 days with mxmtoon, Maia regales us with a pub argument that spiraled into a famous book of trivia...listen to find out which one! She also chats about a favorite music release from 2017. Listen to this episode today and make sure you’re following along with the daily updates @365daysmxmtoon on all platforms.
